Terraform AWS VPC & EC2 Infrastructure
ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project uses Terraform to provision a complete AWS infrastructure that includes:

Custom VPC

Public subnets in multiple Availability Zones

Internet Gateway & Route Tables

Security Group with inbound/outbound rules

Multiple EC2 instances with configurable root volumes

The infrastructure is deployed in the AWS ap-south-1 (Mumbai) region.

