10.0.1.0/24 (ap-south-1a)

10.0.2.0/24 (ap-south-1b)

Internet Gateway

Public Route Table

Security Group (Allow all â€“ demo purpose)

4 EC2 Instances

Jenkins / Ansible Server

Docker / Kubernetes Master

Node1 Server

Node2 Server

