ğŸ”§ Prerequisites

Before running this project, ensure you have:

AWS Account

IAM User with EC2 & VPC permissions

AWS CLI installed and configured

Terraform installed (v1.x recommended)

An existing EC2 Key Pair in AWS

Verify AWS CLI:

aws sts get-caller-identity


Verify Terraform:

terraform version

ğŸ”‘ EC2 Key Pair Requirement

This project expects an existing EC2 Key Pair.

Key pair name used:
key_name = "Priacc_demo"


Make sure this key pair exists in ap-south-1 region.

Check using:

aws ec2 describe-key-pairs --region ap-south-1


If not present, create it from AWS Console or via Terraform.

âš™ï¸ Variables Configuration (terraform.tfvars)
region         = "ap-south-1"
ami_id         = "ami-02b8269d5e85954ef"
key_name       = "Priacc_demo"
instance_type  = "t3.medium"
server1_volume = 20
server2_volume = 15
server3_volume = 10
server4_volume = 10

