âš ï¸ Security Notice

Security Group allows all inbound & outbound traffic (0.0.0.0/0)
âš ï¸ This is NOT recommended for production

Use restricted CIDR blocks for SSH (port 22)

ğŸ“Œ Best Practices Followed

Variables separated using variable.tf

Environment-specific values in terraform.tfvars

Infrastructure as Code (IaC) approach

Region-specific AMI usage

ğŸ“ˆ Possible Enhancements

